data.description: Save thousands a year with no HOA or huge especial assessments taxes on this beautiful move-in ready 3 bed & 2.5 bath home in Lake Elsinore.   The home is located in a well stablished neighborhood on a tree lined street with mountain views.  As you drive up to this 2-story home, you will see its great curb appeal plus a long driveway big enough for RV parking and a 3-car garage!  The one car garage is a pull through garage which means you can drive up your boat or toys up to your backyard very easily for even safer storage or to provide additional storage space in your garage.   As you walk into the home, you are greeted with its enormous, vaulted ceilings throughout the living room plus large windows that will let natural light come through.  A grand staircase leads you upstairs to all your bedrooms while downstairs you will find a cozy kitchen with plenty of cabinets and counterspace, a breakfast nook and family room with a chimney, that can be kept this way or turned into formal dining area!  As you go upstairs it will lead you to two good-sized rooms with wall-to-wall closets and a nice clean restroom to share between the rooms.   The master bedroom offers lots of space with its vaulted ceilings, large restroom, and walk-in closet! As you go downstairs and are ready to host your family events, you will notice a nice, covered porch area with plenty of privacy and greenery provided by its lush palm trees.  There’s plenty of space here to convert this into your dream backyard, there’s already a restroom that can be accessed through the patio, perfect for family gatherings.  The home is located in a great neighborhood with its famous skate zone park and dog park half a block plus skydiving and motorsports park nearby which makes it great for family adventures! Lake Elsinore has lots to offer for those looking for serenity plus outdoor activities with the lake nearby there’s boating, jet skiing, fishing plus plenty of shopping and restaurants nearby makes this home the perfect home for your growing family!
